      • deserializeJson

        public static Object deserializeJson(String json)
                              throws JSONException
        Deserialize a Json string into one of known Deezer objects
        Parameters:
        json - the Json string to deserialize
        Returns:
        the model object corresponding to the given Json, or null if it doesn't match a known model object
        Throws:
        JSONException - if the object can't be deserialized
